{"tid":2516038,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"衛蘭新專輯一日內賣斷市 MV現割脈自殺鏡頭僅網上播","createTime":"2021-05-04T11:23:54.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-04T11:39:59.000Z","uid":38539,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"7874de4751d32d6b3f0353d70abb4c6fcd1c1c2b","tid":2516038,"uid":38539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T11:23:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmcTcT8E5pwkk7dKbVfUR1odBcYgfeM5tFwGEiydmoZGWy?filename=rF00ANr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrF00ANr.png&h=8b54daa6&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n衛蘭（Janice）今日在天后為新專輯舉行分享會，對於新專輯在上星期推出3,000張，一日內已賣斷市，現時要加印2,000張，Janice表示開心又感恩，「喺呢張碟入面，我都參與咗好多，不單止寫歌、編曲，連相都係我自己影，所有嘅訊息都喺我心入面想分享。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmYV6A1H9vocVXUZPL25bv6bCZ4FeMwfuKnZXn42vAj7bJ?filename=RY8Ynsu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRY8Ynsu.png&h=933f7913&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n在活動中亦有展出她拍攝的作品，拍攝對象包括有花圈、露宿者、小朋友等等，Janice透露花了一個月時間去影，「我去影露宿者，佢哋好願意打開個心，同我哋分享佢哋嘅個人故事，其中一個以前係大學教授，佢英文好叻，但變咗露宿者。」<br />\n<br />\n提及她拍攝花圈，Janice指兩個月內有3位朋友因病先後離世，世事難料，會否加速她對結婚的想法？她笑言不會，反而更想多做音樂。對於新歌MV中有割脈自殺的鏡頭，她表示由於過不到電視尺度，所以僅在網上播放，她又指MV中的故事是朋友的親身經歷。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20210504/GQTL3XUDXVDOLMNZWHYHNSL6F4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20210504%2FGQTL3XUDXVDOLMNZWHYHNSL6F4%2F&d=qHuNkoJYq05zO%2BFPSordKw2E5jpmEl9YQHmcT4noKO0%3D&h=816c8b48\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20210504%2FGQTL3XUDXVDOLMNZWHYHNSL6F4%2F&h=38b2cf47\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20210504/GQTL3XUDXVDOLMNZWHYHNSL6F4/</a>"},{"pid":"836112c4c71c2634b590c93592d464c7decfd64c","tid":2516038,"uid":93986,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T11:29:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmbzAGZfaeeWkr5CvQ4gWRSBvhgXZ9EZYVLp4vy